{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/study-blog/cascade/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<p>동일한 요소에 대해 두 개 이상의 CSS 규칙을 적용하는 경우 충돌 발생 → 어떤 CSS 규칙이 적용되는지를 정의하는 방법</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>CSS 적용 우선순위</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>중요도(Importance)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>명시도(Specificity)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>소스 순서(Source order)</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>중요도(Importance)</h1>\n<p>CSS가 어디에 선언 되었는지에 대한 우선순위</p>\n<ol>\n<li>head 요소 내의 style 요소</li>\n<li>head 요소 내의 style 요소 내의 <code class=\"language-text\">@import</code> 문</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;link></code> 로 연결된 CSS 파일</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;link></code> 로 연결된 CSS 파일 내의 <code class=\"language-text\">@import</code> 문</li>\n<li>브라우저 디폴트 스타일시트</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>명시도(Specificity)</h1>\n<p>가중치로 결정</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://specifishity.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">참고: CSS 명시도 가중치</a></p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>!important</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>인라인 스타일</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>id 선택자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* The element with id=\"demo\" */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">#demo</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red 2px solid<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>class 선택자 / attribute 선택자 / pseudo-class</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* All elements with class=\"spacious\" */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">.spacious</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 2em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* &lt;a> elements with a title attribute */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">a[title]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> purple<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* pseudo-class */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">:hover</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\t...\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>type 선택자</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* All &lt;a> elements. */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">a</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>universal selector</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* Selects all elements */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">*</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> green<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>상위 요소에 의해 상속된 속성</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>소스 순서(Source order)</h1>\n<p>동일한 가중치를 갖는 규칙이 두 개 이상인 경우, CSS 에서 마지막에 오는 규칙이 우선</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"html\"><pre class=\"language-html\"><code class=\"language-html\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>This is my heading.<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">h1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> red<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">h1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> blue<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 582px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/79906c35a67c7ce561ea5497776638b7/0b5a5/cascade.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 21.875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAkElEQVR42p2PsQtFcBSFf/+9UZSFCQlFUTIoG4MMdimT2SKl8L1edzJ5vbPczu10Op/ad1hX/tJ5Pv19g5omsCwwDAhDGEfIMmhb6DoIAihLmGfQdchzqCrwfbBtcBzJN42Uqm2DYYA0hTiWkrqWUN/LNU1YFkgS8DxwXfkVBUQRaJoMui5Qv6B9Ud50HIL8ARTTJ7y/f02nAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/79906c35a67c7ce561ea5497776638b7/a59e9/cascade.webp 192w,\n/static/79906c35a67c7ce561ea5497776638b7/0ca9f/cascade.webp 384w,\n/static/79906c35a67